name: Gentlemen by Lemonhaze
description: Gentlemen is a work in progress. The Gentlemen represent the person I want to become for the love of my life. Becoming a gentleman is a lifelong process, a journey that only ends with my death. The Gentlemen are meant to inspire loyalty, integrity, love, and chivalrous behavior. I inscribe them as I see fit, as my soul asks for it. Money alone can't buy it. This is an open series with a max supply of 25 + 1 max per calendar year.
